# Social Media Do’s and Don’ts

##  Do’s
- Maintain a professional profile
- Think before posting content
- Respect others’ opinions
- Use privacy settings wisely
- Share useful and positive information

##  Don’ts
- Do not share personal or sensitive information
- Avoid posting offensive or inappropriate content
- Do not engage in online arguments
- Avoid spreading misinformation
- Do not misuse someone else’s content
